Package org.usfirst.frc3946.UltimateAscent

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OI
    This class is the glue that binds the controls on the physical operator interface to the commands and command groups that allow control of the robot.
    Robot
    The VM is configured to automatically run this class, and to call the functions corresponding to each mode, as described in the IterativeRobot documentation.
    RobotMap
    The RobotMap is a mapping from the ports sensors and actuators are wired into to a variable name.
    XboxJoystick
    Drop in replacement for Joystick using XBOX USB Controller
    XboxJoystick.AxisType
    Represents an analog axis on a joystick.
    XboxJoystick.ButtonType
    Represents a digital button on a joystick.
